name: F- Student [DEMO]
description:
F- Student [DEMO]

You're a poor student, but you have to get all "A"s to get into top 10 universities to get the best job. Unfortunately, you're not the smartest, but maybe you can cheat?

I hope you will enjoy the game!

Now it's just a DEMO.
Please, let me know in the comments if you want to see more levels! I would really appreciate any feedback. 10 COMMENTS AND I'LL MAKE MORE LEVELS!
Also, please, consider donation as it's just my hobby.

I wish you all the best and #staysafe
